{"tid":184180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳洲風暴】水浸搞到蛇蟲鼠蟻盡出 蜘蛛躝上人腳「避難」","createTime":"2017-04-02T15:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T00:10:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d483438946db8d796e6cbc2e4494da84ad4395","tid":184180,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"2017年04月02日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491086553_3e76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491086553_3e76.jpg&h=36dc3d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲昆士蘭連日遭受強烈熱帶氣旋黛比（Debbie）吹襲，除日前有鯊魚被沖到內陸擱淺而死的「奇景」，有人亦拍到大批蛇蟲鼠蟻，為避水浸湧出路面的令人毛管戙畫面，有蜘蛛更爬上人腳「避難」。<br />\n<br />\n吉姆布姆巴（Jimboomba）有居民分享影片，見到蜘蛛、蜈蚣、璧虎等等全都湧出路面的「壯觀」場面。有蜘蛛更爬上他的腳趾，並不斷沿路向上探索，在他的小腿上爬行，希望可避過水浸。<br />\n雖然拍片者的兩隻腳都成為了蟲蟻及蜘蛛的臨時「避難所」，但就沒有將牠們趕走，反而神色自若繼續拍片。<br />\n黛比上周吹襲昆士蘭時，帶來嚴重破壞，更導致數以千計前往大堡礁度假島的遊客要疏散。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170402/56511795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170402%2F56511795&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a94975c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170402%2F56511795&h=cae00b1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170402/56511795</a>"},{"pid":"fb17d773bca56884496e6d34acf5caf51f65d107","tid":184180,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df12a8ceb1e3b0ac73efecf867482da4bd8d3429","tid":184180,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"慘慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可愛小蛛"},{"pid":"1a45a928ae758209c